    "1. Distribution of mabsï¼š\n",
    "\n",
    "- ALï¼šskewness=2.60ï¼Œkurtosis=18.66ï¼Œstrongly right-skewed + heavy-tail\n",
    "- AMï¼šskewness=0.82ï¼Œkurtosis=3.71ï¼Œlight right-skewed\n",
    "- **need to do log transformation**\n",
    "\n",
    "2. one-hot encoding for Neighborhood"
   ]
